*INV:	<do you &-uh> [//] remember this book this book [= The Very Hungry Caterpillar] ?
%mor:	verb|remember-Fin-Imp-S det|this-Def-Dem-Sing noun|book-Acc det|this-Def-Dem-Sing noun|book-Acc ?
